 data crc will educate and assist users with secure computing as outlined by the information security office and the university administrative guides support once service begins please call 5 help or submit a helpsu request for assistance your request will be automatically routed to your field support team crc support is available monday through friday from 8 am to 5 pm rates see the it services client support rates web page getting started to learn how computer resource consulting can support your it needs please contact crc director kim seidler contact information or submit a helpsu request last modified fri 18 nov 2011 at 16 24 pages about this service overview crc service details crc server group crc clients find answers submit a helpsu request stanford answers related pages champ campus hardware maintenance program contract support on call services footer links stanford university helpsu user login stanford university terms of use copyright complaints
